header(class="sticky top-0 z-20 border-b border-zinc-200 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950/95")
    div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 px-5 py-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between")
        div
            div(class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-toolbox")
                span 운영 도구
            h1(class="mt-1 text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 시스템 점검
        button(type="button", (click)="load()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
            i(class="fa-solid fa-rotate-right")
            span 새로고침

main(class="space-y-5 px-5 py-5")
    div(*ngIf="loading()", class="h-32 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400") 정보를 불러오는 중입니다.
    div(*ngIf="error()", class="rounded-md border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-rose-700 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:bg-rose-950/40 dark:text-rose-300") {{error()}}

    div(*ngIf="!loading() && !error()", class="space-y-5")
        section(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 md:grid-cols-3")
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서비스 상태
                p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{health()?.service || '-'}}
                span(class="mt-3 inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(health()?.status)") {{health()?.status || '-'}}
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 버전
                p(class="mt-2 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{health()?.version || '-'}}
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-4 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                p(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 진단 항목
                p(class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{diagnostics.length}}

        section(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
            div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 빠른 점검
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 필요한 항목을 누르면 Docker Infra가 내부 명령을 대신 실행하고 결과만 요약합니다.
            div(class="grid grid-cols-1 divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:divide-x lg:divide-y-0")
                div(*ngFor="let item of diagnostics", class="p-4")
                    div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                        div(class="flex min-w-0 items-start gap-3")
                            div(class="flex h-9 w-9 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200")
                                i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="item.icon")
                            div(class="min-w-0")
                                h3(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{item.title}}
                                p(class="mt-1 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{item.description}}
                        span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(diagnosticStatus(item))") {{diagnosticMessage(item)}}
                    div(class="mt-4 flex items-center justify-between gap-3")
                        button(type="button", (click)="runDiagnostic(item)", [disabled]="runningDiagnostic() === item.id", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                            i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="runningDiagnostic() === item.id ? 'fa-spinner fa-spin' : 'fa-play'")
                            span {{runningDiagnostic() === item.id ? '확인 중' : '점검 실행'}}
                    pre(*ngIf="diagnosticDetail(item)", class="mt-3 max-h-32 overflow-auto whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-md bg-zinc-950 p-3 text-xs text-zinc-50") {{diagnosticDetail(item)}}

        section(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
            div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 고급 명령 목록
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 운영 화면에서는 직접 실행하지 않고, 진단 버튼이나 작업 흐름에서 자동으로 사용합니다.
            div(class="overflow-x-auto")
                table(class="min-w-full divide-y divide-zinc-100 text-sm dark:divide-zinc-800")
                    thead(class="bg-zinc-50 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:bg-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-400")
                        tr
                            th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 항목
                            th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 종류
                            th(class="px-4 py-2 text-left font-semibold") 실행 정책
                    tbody(class="divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800")
                        tr(*ngFor="let command of commands()")
                            td(class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{command.id}}
                            td(class="px-4 py-3 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300") {{command.category}}
                            td(class="px-4 py-3")
                                span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="command.destructive ? statusClass('missing') : statusClass('ok')") {{command.destructive ? '작업 흐름에서만 실행' : '점검 가능'}}
                        tr(*ngIf="commands().length === 0")
                            td(colspan="3", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 등록된 명령이 없습니다.
